{# templates/Welcome/home.html.twig #}
{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Welcome to Vault of Time{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <section class="mbr-section mbr-section--relative mbr-section--fixed-size mbr-after-navbar" id="features1-u" data-rv-view="6" style="background-color: rgb(193, 193, 193);">
        <div class="mbr-section__container container mbr-section__container--std-top-padding" style="padding-top: 93px;">
            <div class="mbr-section__row row">
                <div class="mbr-section__col">
                    {#col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-sm-6">#}
                    <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--center mbr-section__container--middle">
                        <figure class="mbr-figure"><img src="/Assets/Images/bootstrap.png" class="mbr-figure__img"></figure>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--middle">
                        <div class="mbr-header mbr-header--reduce mbr-header--center mbr-header--wysiwyg">
                            <h3 class="mbr-header__text">TIME TRACKING MADE EASY</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--middle">
                        <div class="mbr-article mbr-article--wysiwyg">
                            <p>Vault of Time is a time tracking application that will give you the possibility to track time on iOS, Android, Windows, Mac and a webpage. You have full control over the projects, project types and tasks in the project. You can create companies, departments and/or teams and include or exclude employees without regards to who they are or where they work. VoT can easily accomodate time tracking for your hired consultants and more.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mbr-section__container mbr-section__container--last" style="padding-bottom: 93px;">
                        <div class="mbr-buttons mbr-buttons--center"><a href="https://mobirise.com" class="mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default">LEARN MORE</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}